Perfect ‚Äî you caught that at exactly the right point üëè

Since your Angular app is standalone (no AppModule), each component must import its own dependencies, even if other components already did.
So, just like we fixed it in travell.ts, we‚Äôll fix it in both travel-details.ts and approvals.ts by importing CommonModule.

Let‚Äôs correct both files üëá


